  focus: "This lesson examines how sensitivity analysis and Monte Carlo simulation are applied to residual development appraisals to stress-test key variables. Understanding how to quantify and communicate risk in appraisals is critical for advising developer clients, funders, and planning authorities — and is a common area of APC questioning at Level 3.",
